    <item>
      <title>瑞银 Haefele 称美联储将降息 25 个基点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-29/fed-set-for-25bp-rate-cut-says-ubs-haefele-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银全球财富管理首席投资官 Mark Haefele 表示，除非美国经济进一步疲软，否则美联储将在 9 月降息 25 个基点。他在彭博简报中接受了 Manus Cranny 的采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-29/fed-set-for-25bp-rate-cut-says-ubs-haefele-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 10:02:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Delivery Hero 计划在迪拜为其中东子公司 Talabat 进行 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/talabat-ipo-delivery-hero-eyes-dubai-listing-for-middle-eastern-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Delivery Hero SE 正考虑将其中东子公司 Talabat 在迪拜证券交易所上市，以期从海湾地区的上市热潮中获益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/talabat-ipo-delivery-hero-eyes-dubai-listing-for-middle-eastern-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:53:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾通过储备灵活性简化人寿保险公司的外汇管理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/taiwan-eases-life-insurer-fx-management-with-reserve-flexibility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾金融监督管理委员会正在采取措施，减轻寿险公司的外汇对冲成本负担。由于当地和美国的利率差距很大，外汇对冲成本有所上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/taiwan-eases-life-insurer-fx-management-with-reserve-flexibility</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:52:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元普遍疲软，人民币抹平 2024 年跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/china-s-yuan-erases-2024-s-losses-amid-broad-dollar-weakness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期资本将回流中国，且美联储预计将于下个月启动政策宽松周期，中国在岸人民币今年上涨，抹平了失地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/china-s-yuan-erases-2024-s-losses-amid-broad-dollar-weakness</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:27:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凉鞋需求强劲，Birkenstock 确认前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/birkenstock-affirms-outlook-amid-strong-demand-for-sandals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Birkenstock Holding Plc 确认了其 2024 年财务目标，并报告了强劲的盈利增长，因为消费者抢购更多高端凉鞋和木屐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/birkenstock-affirms-outlook-amid-strong-demand-for-sandals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>董事会考虑发行红股，信实股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ambani-s-reliance-to-consider-one-on-one-bonus-share-issue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[信实工业有限公司 (Reliance Industries Ltd.) 表示，将考虑发行红股 — — 这是该公司七年来的首次 — — 该公司亿万富翁董事长穆克什·安巴尼 (Mukesh Ambani) 希望在继续向面向消费者的业务多元化发展的过程中吸引小股东。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ambani-s-reliance-to-consider-one-on-one-bonus-share-issue</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 08:26:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国暂缓征收关税，人头马和保乐力加股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/pernod-says-us-china-sales-will-remain-soft-this-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示至少目前不会对欧盟白兰地征收临时关税，此后人头马君度集团 (Remy Cointreau SA) 和保乐力加集团 (Pernod Ricard SA) 的股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/pernod-says-us-china-sales-will-remain-soft-this-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 05:27:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
